# Sellsuki Design System — Cursor Rules
# Full spec: https://sellsukidesignsystemv12.vercel.app/ai-rules.md

## Setup (REQUIRED — must do FIRST)
```bash
npm install @uxuissk/design-system@0.8.4
npm install @uxuissk/design-tokens@0.1.1  # optional tokens
```

```tsx
// main.tsx or App.tsx — FIRST LINE, before everything else
import "@uxuissk/design-system/styles.css";
import { DSButton, DSInput, Card, AdvancedDataTable, TopNavbar, Sidebar } from "@uxuissk/design-system";
```

⚠️ WITHOUT the CSS import: fonts will be wrong (no DB HeaventRounded), all size tokens will be undefined, components will look broken.

## Font — DB HeaventRounded for ALL text
- NEVER use Inter, system-ui, or any other font
- Font is bundled in the npm package — no Google Fonts needed
- Apply to: headings, body, labels, buttons, badges, nav, table, sidebar

## Typography Tokens
| Token | Size | Weight | Usage |
|-------|------|--------|-------|
| `var(--text-h1)` | 48px | 400 | Page hero |
| `var(--text-h2)` | 40px | 400 | Page title |
| `var(--text-h3)` | 28px | 700 | Section header |
| `var(--text-h4)` | 24px | 500 | Card header |
| `var(--text-p)` | 20px | 400 | Body text |
| `var(--text-label)` | 18px | 400 | Form labels |
| `var(--text-button)` | 18px | 600 | Buttons, badges |
| `var(--text-caption)` | 14px | 400 | Captions, hints |

⚠️ MINIMUM font size: 14px (`var(--text-caption)`) — never use smaller

## Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| Primary | `#32a9ff` | Buttons, links, brand |
| Primary hover | `#1b8bf5` | Hover states |
| Text primary | `#1f2937` | Headings, body |
| Text secondary | `#6b7280` | Muted text |
| Border | `#e5e7eb` | Dividers, cards |
| Surface | `#f9fafb` | Page background |
| Success | `#059669` | Success states |
| Warning | `#d97706` | Warning states |
| Danger | `#e11d48` | Error, destructive |

Use CSS variables: `var(--primary)`, `var(--foreground)`, `var(--border)` etc. NEVER hardcode hex.

## Layout Pattern — AppShell (preferred)
```tsx
import { AppShell, sellsukiBrandConfig, FeaturePageScaffold } from "@uxuissk/design-system";

<AppShell
  product={sellsukiBrandConfig}
  user={currentUser}
  navResolver={myNavResolver}
  activeItemId="orders"
  onNavigate={(item) => router.push(item.href!)}
>
  <FeaturePageScaffold
    layout="list"
    header={<PageHeader title="Orders" primaryAction={{ label: "Create order" }} />}
    content={<DSTable ... />}
  />
</AppShell>
```

## Button Rules
- Variants: `primary` | `secondary` | `outline` | `ghost` | `destructive` | `link`
- Sizes: `sm` (32px) | `md` (36px) | `lg` (40px) | `xl` (44px)
- **MAX 1 primary button per view**

## Components (60+ total)
Data Entry: DSButton, IconButton, ButtonGroup, DSInput, DSTextarea, DSCheckbox, CheckboxGroup, DSRadio, RadioGroup, Switch, Dropdown, DatePicker, DateRangePicker, TimePicker, DateTimePicker, SearchField, ColorPicker, FileUpload, TagInput, Rating, TransferList, NumberInput, OTPInput, RepeatableFieldList, RichTextEditor
Data Display: DSTable, AdvancedDataTable, Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter, StatCard, Statistic, Badge, Tag, Avatar, AvatarGroup, Timeline, Tree, EmptyState, Skeleton, ImageGallery, ThumbnailCell
Charts: LineChart, AreaChart, BarChart, DonutChart, MiniSparkline
Choice: ChoiceCard, ChoiceCardGroup, RadioCard
Navigation: TopNavbar, Sidebar, Breadcrumb, Tabs, Stepper, Pagination
Feedback: Alert, Modal, Drawer, ConfirmDialog, Notification, toast, ToastContainer, Tooltip, Popover, ProgressBar, Spinner
Layout: Divider, Menu, ImagePreview, PageHeader, FilterBar, FeaturePageScaffold, ScaffoldSection, ScaffoldKPIRow
Form: FormField, FormLabel, FormError, FormHelperText
Shell: AppShell, AppShellSkeleton, AppShellProvider, useAppShell, useBreadcrumbs

## Rules
1. Always import CSS first — `import "@uxuissk/design-system/styles.css"`
2. Use DS components — never create custom buttons, inputs, modals
3. DB HeaventRounded for ALL text — never Inter
4. Min font size 14px — never smaller
5. Max 1 primary button per view
6. Handle loading (Skeleton), empty (EmptyState), error (Alert) states
7. Use only palette colors — no random hex values
8. Flat design — no heavy shadows, no gradients

